item.title: About
item.description: I am a Ph.D. student at University of Genoa, Italy with Mechanics, Robotics and Measurements curriculum , Italy. I majored in Advanced Robotics from an Erasmus Mundus program named European Master on Advanced Robotics+ with dual degrees from Ecole Centrale de Nantes, France and University of Genoa, Italy. I obtained my Bachelors in Mechanical Engineering with Gold Medal from Sri Manakula Vinayagar Engineering College, India.. While awaiting my admittance to master’s program aboard, I worked as Assistant System Engineer at Tata Consultancy Services, India developing Java based API for The Home Depot, USA.

item.title: Contact
